<div id="register">
<h4>Create a New User</h4>
Creation of a user means that you agree with the rules and other legal bits of the site.  Chief amoung these rules is only one user per person.  Users may have multiple characters and participate in multiple games.  Only "power users" can create games.  Please remember your password, as it will be stored in our database, and no one can tell you what it is if you lose it.  Thank you.<br/><br/>
<form action="{URL}user/register" method="post">
<label for="name">Name: </label><input type="text" class="box" name="name" size="20" id="name" maxlength="50"/><br/>
<label for="pass">Password: </label><input type="password" class="box" name="password" size="15" id="pass"/><br/>
<label for="pass2">Retype Password: </label><input type="password" class="box" name="password2" size="15" id="pass2"/><br/>
<label for="email">Email: </label><input type="text" class="box" name="email" size="20" id="email" maxlength="100"/><br/>
<label for="email2">Retype Email: </label><input type="text" class="box" name="email2" size="20" id="email2" maxlength="100"/><br/>
<input type="submit" value="Create User"/>
</form>
</div>